What is DOM => Document (HTML Document) Object Model. Document has elements like Paragraph, Hyperlinks etc. So DOM represent all this elements as Objects. And all these objects are stored in Docuemnt Object.

Where is Document Object present => javascript programs are executed in run time environment. When we run a js program in browser, the run time is browser. Every run time environment has a global object, in case of 
                                    browser the rum time environment is Window Obbject. This Window Object contains the Docuemnt Object.



                                